{"tid":1139571,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇戲遇到d死廢中廢老真係唔屌唔得架","createTime":"2019-05-05T10:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T13:19:36.000Z","uid":70786,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77365a11334bde21e2fa65f7b0ea69a0b38d21a6","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:54:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早幾日去睇孟買酒店<br />\n一早買定皇帝位諗住可以歎足全場<br />\n點知有兩條死廢中兩公婆坐我隔籬<br />\n遲入場都算啦<br />\n坐低冇耐就話「下乜印度戲嚟架？是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我心諗孟買唔喺印度係邊度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個死廢嬸坐我側邊<br />\n一路睇一路依偎住佢老公做旁述<br />\n見D恐怖分子射人就「嘩痴線架」<br />\n電影海報大大隻字寫住恐襲你expect d乜<br />\n孟買酒店唔通係孟母三遷續集講孟子酒店風雲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到D恐怖分子混入人群入酒店佢就「哎呀佢地幾個都係架」<br />\n坐我隔籬個女仔頂唔順就Shhhh咗佢一聲<br />\n點知條臭閪都唔收聲<br />\nD恐怖分子係酒店大開殺戒就不停「痴線架」「好恐怖呀」<br />\n我忍唔住就爆咗句「唔該唔好嘈啦好冇呀」<br />\n個八婆俾我嚇親，講完一句「唔好意思」<br />\n同佢老公咬咗陣耳仔，之後就掉位坐佢老公另一面<br />\n我眼角望到佢老公間唔中就睥鳩我<br />\n好似係我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到完場著燈，條死廢中想睇清楚我咩樣睥鳩住我<br />\n我就屌鳩佢「睥完未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我隔籬個女仔又幫口「幾廿歲人睇套戲仲嘈過d小朋友」<br />\n條死廢中嬲到出煙又唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb99e6ae34a35893f35b6f91c6df9b5d4b5c915","tid":1139571,"uid":31355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"大快人心"},{"pid":"34cd36aab6b1b9da8ce72e564e2f07426af70930","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"發覺愈嚟愈多廢中為過日辰<br />\n恃住自己睇戲有折<br />\n劇情簡介都唔睇就買飛入場<br />\n成日睇到一半唔岩睇就走<br />\n<br />\n好心就取消廢中廢老優惠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a81c36ea3581a5be8c43f4a05657c84b6fd45b5","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"D廢中點解咁喜歡旁述<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟係咩心態？<br />\n覺得自己俾咗錢就可以當自己屋企？"},{"pid":"e63d19cafc09c5d837edb0ab8ed01bd0e6d0d6fd","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"又諗翻起God bless America入面戲院場戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzRWlT_KjUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzRWlT_KjUw&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e9f828bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzRWlT_KjUw</a><br />\nd死廢老係溫室生存得太耐真係唔驚會有癲佬懲罰佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b182918e818e5882fb15d6b0c0b7a413d94250","tid":1139571,"uid":74332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"其實好似的士判官咁<br />\n拍返套戲院屠夫 教下班撚屌睇戲禮儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036a3551383a0cb0d2cb57a211499a87e184ad45","tid":1139571,"uid":187893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"有冇識到隔離個女仔？"},{"pid":"5c66c6d94ef476106c3e8db93a1772f4e1f6b751","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036a3551383a0cb0d2cb57a211499a87e184ad45","tid":1139571,"uid":187893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"有冇識到隔離個女仔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861a3dce9ac77f6feacdf5bb9f932aa69658c7f6","tid":1139571,"uid":71180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c66c6d94ef476106c3e8db93a1772f4e1f6b751","tid":1139571,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036a3551383a0cb0d2cb57a211499a87e184ad45","tid":1139571,"uid":187893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"有冇識到隔離個女仔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T